This library creates an XDG-compliant application menu
using the garcon library.

to build it, you will need:
 - GLib
 - libgarcon
 - qmake

with these dependencies compiled, run:

```
qmake
make
sh install.sh
```
to build and install the library. After installing the
library, you can test it by going into the "test" folder
and running ```qmake && make``` to compile the test program,
and ```./test``` to run in.
